Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image classification and face recognition algorithms. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the dataset is extracted from public available images on website and online videos on iQiYi company. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is possible as the paper mentions the annotation process of the dataset. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is possible as the paper proposes a dataset fusion method to improve the performance of cartoon recognition task. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is possible as the paper evaluates the performance of recognition algorithms compared to human performance.
